{"text_id":47782,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," present"," TR","UF","AS",","," a"," novel"," wavelet","-","based"," algorithm"," for"," the"," rapid"," detection"," of"," planetary"," trans","its","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," for"," efficient"," and"," accurate"," methods"," for"," transit"," detection",","," given"," the"," increasing"," volume"," of"," astronomical"," data"," being"," generated"," by"," modern"," surveys","."," The"," traditional"," box","-","fitting"," method",","," while"," widely"," used",","," can"," be"," computationally"," expensive"," and"," may"," struggle"," to"," detect"," shallow"," trans","its"," or"," those"," with"," complex"," shapes","."," To"," address"," these"," challenges",","," we"," developed"," TR","UF","AS",","," which"," employs"," wavelet"," decomposition"," to"," decompose"," light"," curves"," into"," their"," frequency"," components",","," enabling"," the"," detection"," of"," transit","-","like"," signals"," at"," various"," scales",".","\n\n","Through"," extensive"," simulations",","," we"," demonstrated"," that"," TR","UF","AS"," can"," detect"," transit","-","like"," signals"," with"," high"," sensitivity"," and"," specificity",","," even"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," significant"," noise","."," We"," compared"," TR","UF","AS"," to"," the"," box","-","fitting"," method"," and"," found"," that"," it"," could"," detect"," transit"," signals"," with"," comparable"," accuracy"," but"," with"," a"," significant"," reduction"," in"," computational"," cost","."," Furthermore",","," TR","UF","AS"," was"," shown"," to"," be"," robust"," against"," various"," types"," of"," stellar"," variability"," and"," instrumental"," noise",","," making"," it"," a"," promising"," tool"," for"," the"," analysis"," of"," large"," astronomical"," datasets",".","\n\n","In"," addition",","," TR","UF","AS"," can"," provide"," estimates"," of"," the"," transit","'","s"," 